### CheckPoint — Admin Reviews endpoints
### Requires an ADMIN account. See admin-users.http for the login request.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_HERE

### List all reviews (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reviews?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List reported reviews (moderation queue)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reviews/reported?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List the reports filed against a specific review
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reviews/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/reports?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete a review
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/reviews/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
